<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">أوّلاً:</span> أوزانُ الثُّلاثيّ المُلْحَقِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أ-<span class="c5"> المُلْحَقُ بالرُّبَاعِيِّ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١- ما أُلْحِقَ بـ <span class="c2">(فَعْلَ)</span> :<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>ويُعَدّ هذا الوزن أكثرَ أوزان الرّباعيّ إلحاقاً به؛ لأنَّه يقع للأسماء والأفعال؛ نحو <span class="c2">(جَعْفَرٍ)</span> و <span class="c2">(دَحْرَجَ)</span> فممَّا ألحق به:<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(فَعْلَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(جَلْبَبَ)</span> في الأفعال، و <span class="c2">(قَرْدَدٍ)</span> في الأسماء.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>و <span class="c2">(فَوْعَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(جَوْرَبَ)</span> في الأفعال، و <span class="c2">(كَوْكَبٍ)</span> في الأسماء.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>و <span class="c2">(فَيْعَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(سَيْطَرَ)</span> في الأفعال، و <span class="c2">(فَيْصَلٍ)</span> في الأسماء.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>و <span class="c2">(فَعْوَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(هَرْوَلَ)</span> في الأفعال، و <span class="c2">(جَرْوَلٍ)</span> في الأسماء.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>و <span class="c2">(فَعْيَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(شَرْيَفَ)</span> .<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>و <span class="c2">(فَعْنَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(قَلْنَسَه)</span> إذا ألبسه القلنسوة.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>و <span class="c2">(فَعْلَى)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(سَلْقَى)</span> في قولهم: سَلْقَاهُ على ظَهْرِه،<span class="c5"> أي:</span> مَدَّه.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>و <span class="c2">(فَنْعَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(سَنْبَلَ)</span> الرّجلُ الثّوبَ،<span class="c5"> بمعنى:</span> أَسْبَلَه، و <span class="c2">(عَنْسَلٍ)</span> في الأسماء.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>و <span class="c2">(فَعْلَن)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(رَعْشَنٍ)</span> وهو المرتعش.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>و <span class="c2">(سَفْعَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(سَنْبَسَ)</span> بمعنى: نَبَسَ، إذا أسرعَ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>و <span class="c2">(فَعْلَس)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(خَلْبَسَ)</span> بمعنى: خَلَبَه؛<span class="c5"> أي:</span> فَتَنَه.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>٢- ما أُلْحِقَ بـ <span class="c2">(فُعْلُل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(جُؤْذُر)</span> :<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(فُعْلُل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(قُعْدُد)</span> .<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>و <span class="c2">(فُعْلُم)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(زُرْقُم)</span> .<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>